snippet.title: DIDDY - Steam Offical Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Destroy a dark party in Diddy's mansion. Gather your comrades Eminam and 51 Cent and save Justin B from Diddy! You can destroy the party with your friends by experiencing co-op.
